        "Perito"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我添加了这两条转移。接下来Perito接受任务后进入EnProgreso，完成工作后提交到EnRevision，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AsignadoPerito",
        "EnProgreso",
        "EnRevision",
        "Perito accepts",
        "Work submitted"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是的，但EnRevision需要有两个出口：如果需要修改，回到Observaciones状态让Perito修正；如果通过审批，则进入Completado。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EnRevision",
        "Observaciones",
        "Completado",
        "Needs changes",
        "Approved"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Observaciones之后是回到EnProgreso重新工作，而不是直接回到EnRevision吧？",
